In 2016 a $60M Ethereum DAO hack was such a big deal that the whole crypto world gasped and forked Ethereum into $ETH and $ETC.

In 2022 it seems that every other week there is a $100M+ hack and the crypto world just shrugs and moves on.

content:
1⃣ Accounts in Etherium 
There are two types of accounts in Etherium - a) externally owned i.e. owned by you and b) contract accounts ("smart contracts"). 
Your "wallet" on metamask is simply a UI to an externally owned account. 

#Accounts #Ethereum
